Employee Management System


1- fetch the data,

2-create a dummy structure to append data from api,

3- create a sorting

4- pagination


The Employee Management System is a web application that allows users to view and manage employee data. Users can filter employees by department and gender, sort them by salary, and navigate through paginated results.

Features
Filtering: Users can filter employees by department and gender to view specific groups of employees.


Sorting: Employees can be sorted by salary in ascending or descending order.


Pagination: Results are paginated to improve usability and performance.


Responsive Design: The application is designed to work seamlessly across various devices and screen sizes.